<li><a href="http://www.ifp.org" class="external text" title="http://www.ifp.org" rel="nofollow">Independent Feature Project</a> <a href="/wiki/IFP_(Independent_Feature_Project)" title="IFP (Independent Feature Project)" class="mw-redirect">IFP</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.workbookproject.com" class="external text" title="http://www.workbookproject.com" rel="nofollow">Workbook Project</a> an open source project for independent filmmakers <a href="/w/index.php?title=Workbook_Project&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Workbook Project (page does not exist)">Workbook Project</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.film.com/festivals" class="external text" title="http://www.film.com/festivals" rel="nofollow">Independent Film Page</a>on <a href="/w/index.php?title=Film.com&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Film.com (page does not exist)">Film.com</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.talentcircle.co.uk" class="external text" title="http://www.talentcircle.co.uk" rel="nofollow">talentcircle.co.uk</a> Leading resource and community for independent filmmakers</li>
<li><a href="http://independentpictures.com/" class="external text" title="http://independentpictures.com/" rel="nofollow">IndependentPictures.com</a> - Share and review indie films and find talents for your next project!</li>
<li><a href="http://www.independentfilmdistribution.com" class="external text" title="http://www.independentfilmdistribution.com" rel="nofollow">independentfilmdistribution.com</a> Listing of leading independent film distributors</li>
<li><a href="http://nomadsland.com" class="external text" title="http://nomadsland.com" rel="nofollow">NomadsLand</a> - Distribution and resources for social issue filmmakers.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cobravision.co.uk" class="external text" title="http://www.cobravision.co.uk" rel="nofollow">CobraVision</a> - Independent films international competition.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.filmmakingstuff.com" class="external text" title="http://www.filmmakingstuff.com" rel="nofollow">Filmmaking Stuff</a> - A resource for new Independent Filmmakers.</li>
</ul>
